'''Earth science''' (also known as '''geoscience''', '''the geosciences''', or '''the Earth Sciences'''), is an all-embracing term for the sciences related to the planet [[Earth (planet)|Earth]]. It is arguably a special case in [[planetary science]], being the only known [[life]]-bearing planet known to [[Homo sapiens sapiens|Homo sapiens]]. There are both [[reductionist]] and [[holistic]] approaches to Earth science.
